{\an8}《诉讼双雄》前情提要

15
00:00:02,440 --> 00:00:03,560
我可不欠哈维什么
I don't owe Harvey shit.

16
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:04,570
也许是他还了我的清白
He may have gotten me out,

17
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:06,140
但当初他也是卡梅隆的帮凶
but he and Cameron put me in there in the first place.

18
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:07,460
没错  你不欠哈维的
You're right, you don't owe Harvey,

19
00:00:07,590 --> 00:00:09,420
但你欠我的  因为你被冤枉的事
but you do owe me because I didn't have anything

20
00:00:09,420 --> 00:00:10,400
跟我没有关系
to do with putting you in there,

21
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,940
